Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch the following video
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that contains heartfelt comments
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,from persecuted brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and sisters in Russia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and see why we have no reason\Nto fear persecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was horrified when several masked officers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,broke down two doors and burst into the home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,where the meeting was being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything happened at once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,—loud sounds, noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the order:\N“Everyone sit on the floor!”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was overcome with fear when they put me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in handcuffs, placed me in the police van,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and took me to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn’t know how long
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be there and what was awaiting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was being interrogated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid that I might be unfaithful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to Jehovah and let my brothers down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After being detained, I was mostly afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,about what I would face in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,—whom I would encounter, how to act,\Nhow others would treat me—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When one of the officers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,began to describe\Nhow bad life is behind bars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagined that behind the officer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stood an angel just like the one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,who supported Daniel in the illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This helped me to calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and not to panic or be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how Jehovah supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At the first court appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was brought out,\Nthe brothers’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,impelled them to show support somehow,\Nand they began applauding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How that encouraged me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that they were with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fervent and sincere prayers to Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,helped me to cope with these fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isaiah 30:15
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,gave me much support.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that tranquility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and trust in Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are now the most important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,made things much easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We took the elevator down to the first floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the doors opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and there stood a large crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of our brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,—and they all began clapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw that, my emotions just welled up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got a lump in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt as if I had wings;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the “great cloud of witnesses.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed to Jehovah\Nfor calmness, courage, and wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he help me\Nnot to bring reproach on his holy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost immediately,\N“the peace of God” came over me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The unpleasant sensations did not go away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was no longer afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,While overcoming our fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife and I tried to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in service every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don’t concentrate on yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but focus on helping others, fear disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that helped me\Nto cope with my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the situation\Nthrough Jehovah’s eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing what will happen next
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is not the end of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but only a difficult phase\Nthrough which you can pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was helped to cope with my fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,by the words of the song:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,“Take one day at a time;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“leave tomorrow until tomorrow;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,peace is what I find.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood that it was important
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to solve problems as they came up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and not to be troubled\Nby what might never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is interesting;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that is, in principle, fear can be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,inside a person, and if someone is afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you overcome this fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get the fear under your control?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you overcome this surge of negativity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And when my heart persuaded me to get scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then I started to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed to Jehovah to give me courage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and not be afraid of anyone or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I still say to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‘Feliks, do not fear anybody\Nor anything except Jehovah!’
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear brothers and sisters,\NI really appreciate your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m very happy for all your letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for all your thoughts, for all your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to do my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and I try to serve Jehovah\Nin the best way that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do that forever!
